ztmxInGetPdus.name: ztmxInGetPdus

ztmxInGetNextPdus.name: ztmxInGetNextPdus
ztmxInGetNextPdus.description: The total number of GetNext PDUs received by the TMUX process. These are probably strayed PDUs as the TMUX process is bound to the TRAP port.

ztmxInSetPdus.name: ztmxInSetPdus
ztmxInSetPdus.description: The total number of Set PDUs received by the TMUX process. These are probably strayed PDUs as the TMUX process is bound to the TRAP port.

ztmxInGetResponsePdus.name: ztmxInGetResponsePdus
ztmxInGetResponsePdus.description: The total number of GetResponse PDUs received by the TMUX process. These are probably strayed PDUs as the TMUX process is bound to the TRAP port.

ztmxInTrapPdus.name: ztmxInTrapPdus
ztmxInTrapPdus.description: The total number of Trap PDUs received by the TMUX process.

ztmxInColdStartTraps.description: The total number of Trap PDUs received by the TMUX process that report reinitiation but the configuration of the sender may change.

ztmxInLinkDownTraps.description: The total number of Trap PDUs received by the TMUX process that report a failure in one of the agent's links.

ztmxInEgpNeighborLossTraps.name: ztmxInEgpNeighborLossTraps
ztmxInEgpNeighborLossTraps.description: The total number of Trap PDUs received by the TMUX process that report an exterior gateway protocol neighbor is lost.

ztmxInEnterpriseSpecificTraps.name: ztmxInEnterpriseSpecificTraps
ztmxInEnterpriseSpecificTraps.description: The total number of Trap PDUs received by the TMUX process that report an enterprise specific event.

ztmxProcAgent.name: ztmxProcAgent

ztmxProcProgramFileName.description: String showing the proram file name of the TMUX process.

ztmxProcEmsWriteTotal.name: ztmxProcEmsWriteTotal
ztmxProcEmsWriteTotal.description: Total count of write operations to the EMS collector process. Each write operation attempts to send a trap event to the EMS collector.

ztmxProcEmsWriteErrors.name: ztmxProcEmsWriteErrors
ztmxProcEmsWriteErrors.description: Count of write operations to the EMS collector process that did not complete normally. It's likely that the trap event that was sent with such operation was not successfully stored in the EMS database.
